  <entry>
    <title>Hexo-隱藏文章</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/03/09/Hexo-HidePost/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/03/09/Hexo-HidePost/</id>
    <published>2022-03-09T07:14:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-09T15:45:56.769Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="下載套件"><a href="#下載套件" class="headerlink" title="下載套件"></a>下載套件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-hide-posts --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="config-yml增加設定"><a href="#config-yml增加設定" class="headerlink" title="_config.yml增加設定"></a>_config.yml增加設定</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># hexo-hide-posts</span></span><br><span class="line">hide_posts:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 可以改成其他你喜欢的名字</span></span><br><span class="line">  filter: hidden</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 指定你想要传递隐藏文章的 generator，比如让所有隐藏文章在存档页面可见</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 常见的 generators 有：index, tag, category, archive, sitemap, feed, etc.</span></span><br><span class="line">  public_generators: []</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 为隐藏的文章添加 noindex meta 标签，阻止搜索引擎收录</span></span><br><span class="line">  noindex: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="文章設定"><a href="#文章設定" class="headerlink" title="文章設定"></a>文章設定</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hidden: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>參考網站：</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.0412.cyou/type/heyc.html">hexo 隐藏文章插件 hexo+next-hidden-post</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
